<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Coming Soon — AlgoVisuals</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style1.css" />

  <style>
    body {
      background: #020202;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 180px;
    }

    .coming-container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 80px 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1919 0%, #0f0f0f 100%);
      border-radius: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 34px #0009;
    }

    .coming-title {
      font-size: 85px;
      font-weight: 900;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3B82F6 0%, #A855F7 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .coming-sub {
      font-size: 26px;
      color: #9c9c9c;
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 0 auto 45px auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .soon-box {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 22px 38px;
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3B82F6 0%, #A855F7 100%);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 50px;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="coming-container">
  <h1 class="coming-title">Coming Soon</h1>
  <p class="coming-sub">
    We're building something exciting to enhance your algorithm learning experience.<br>
    This page will be available shortly.
  </p>

  <div class="soon-box">Stay Tuned</div>

  <p class="footer-note">© 2025 AlgoVisuals. All rights reserved.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>